    <h1>Transactional Email</h1>
    <p class="description">Automated messages sent to one person in direct response to an action they have taken. Order confirmations, password resets, and receipts are transactional emails — they have the <strong>highest open rates of any email type</strong> and are essential to product trust.</p>
